{"tid":1191564,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（保險佬入）想買bupa 醫保","createTime":"2019-06-08T03:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T12:18:32.000Z","uid":7442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac5ab7db549b763862bd12b9d728a177403ae83","tid":1191564,"uid":7442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n係bupa官網見到佢個卓康健好似幾岩 <br />\n但有幾個問題想請教下 我拎大房計<br />\n1.佢基本保障係19萬5 如果我加左佢個全數賠償保障我只要係佢list內醫院到睇病就可以全數賠番？但最高就22萬5？<br />\n2.承上題 如果我唔加佢個全數賠償保障 我係佢list內/非list內最多只係一年賠19萬5？<br />\n3.附加醫療保障係for 每年個數claim爆左用？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bupa.com.hk/-/media/files/pdf/by-product/carepro-carekid/carepro-brochure-sob.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bupa.com.hk%2F-%2Fmedia%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Fby-product%2Fcarepro-carekid%2Fcarepro-brochure-sob.pdf&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW89%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=139eee53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bupa.com.hk/-/media/files/pdf/by-product/carepro-carekid/carepro-brochure-sob.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎sales 留TG 請利申埋邊間<br />\n主要想買醫保 budget 每年2k-4K"},{"pid":"034e16346ecb8d421be47fc544e2a51f774e18d1","tid":1191564,"uid":27516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:12:10.000Z","msg":"買bupa together 抵啲<br />\n已經係full cover, 每年仲送身體檢查。"},{"pid":"b42936ba3ec755ac76f65fa16d9c2eca6b2f899e","tid":1191564,"uid":7442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"034e16346ecb8d421be47fc544e2a51f774e18d1","tid":1191564,"uid":27516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:12:10.000Z","msg":"買bupa together 抵啲<br />\n已經係full cover, 每年仲送身體檢查。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"又好似係 不過單人買得25萬"},{"pid":"02edcc33b9a2239fd88d9071053242aa78bbde90","tid":1191564,"uid":27516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b42936ba3ec755ac76f65fa16d9c2eca6b2f899e","tid":1191564,"uid":7442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"034e16346ecb8d421be47fc544e